message.content:
1. Lanreotide Autogel® 120 mg is administered every 4–8 weeks.
2. Lanreotide microparticles 30 mg is administered every 7–14 days.
3. Lanreotide Autogel® 120 mg is at least as effective as lanreotide microparticles 30 mg in treating acromegaly.
4. Lanreotide Autogel® 120 mg is as well tolerated as lanreotide microparticles 30 mg in treating acromegaly.

messages.content:
